<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="no-problem">no problem</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>[表示乐于相助或事情容易做]没问题：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>— How about meeting at the nearby restaurant? 
在附近的餐馆见面如何？</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>— No problem. 
没问题。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>没关系；不客气：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>— Thanks for the ride. 
谢谢你载我一程。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>— No problem. 
不客气。</p></div>

<h3 id="problem-question">辨析 problem, question</h3>
<p>二者都可译作“问题”。<br />
<strong>problem</strong>  指客观存在等待解决的“问题”，强调困难。
<strong>question</strong> 指对某事怀疑而提出等待回答的“问题”，着重疑惑和不能断定。</p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I’d like to put a question to the speaker. 
我想向发言人提一个问题。</p></div></div>